I"¤°<p>Hydejack offers a few additional features to markup your content.
Donâ€™t worry, these are merely CSS classes added with kramdownâ€™s <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">{:...}</code> syntax,
so that your content remains compatible with other Jekyll themes.</p>

